            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://kotaku.com/how-long-is-indiana-jones-great-circle-xbox-game-pass-1851708781<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/machine-games-is-making-an-indiana-jones-game-1846042044&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/machine-games-is-making-an-indiana-jones-game-1846042044"><em>Indiana Jones and the Great Circle</em></a></span><em> </em>is nearly here. The big first-person action-puzzler arrives on Xbox and PC next month and if  you’ve been wondering just how big Indy’s next digital adventure will be, well, we don’t have a specific number yet, but it sounds big. </p><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><div data-video-id="195358" data-monetizable="true" data-position="sidebar" data-video-title="Blasphemous 2 Developer Interview" data-video-blog-id="9" data-video-network="kotaku" data-video-duration="297" data-playlist="195358,196358,195922" data-current="195358"><div><p>Blasphemous 2 Developer Interview</p></div><video disablepictureinpicture="" muted="" playsinline="" width="100%" height="100%" crossorigin="anonymous" preload="none"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/195358/195358_240p.mp4" label="240p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/195358/195358_480p.mp4" label="480p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/195358/195358_720p.mp4" label="720p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/195358/195358_1080p.mp4" label="1080p" type="video/mp4"><track kind="captions" label="English" src="https://kinja.com/api/videoupload/caption/20816.vtt" srclang="en"></video><div><ul><li data-label="">Off</li><li data-label="English">English</li></ul></div></div><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><p><strong>Pre-order <em>Indiana Jones and the Great Circle: </em></strong><span><a data-ga="[]" href="https://www.amazon.com/Indiana-Jones-Great-Circle-Xbox-X/dp/B0DDRCNCHC/ref=sr_1_1?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://kotaku.com/how-long-is-indiana-jones-great-circle-xbox-game-pass-1851708781&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim" data-vtas-click="self:InlineUrl:inline-url-postbody" data-amazonasin="B0DDRCNCHC" data-amazontag="kinjakotakulink-20">Amazon</a></span> | <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://howl.link/o5gjvwl4kpjle&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://howl.link/o5gjvwl4kpjle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Best Buy</a></span> | <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://humblebundleinc.sjv.io/c/379647/2059850/25796?subId1=KT-&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Findiana-jones-and-the-great-circle%3Fhmb_source%3Dsearch_bar&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://humblebundleinc.sjv.io/c/379647/2059850/25796?subId1=KT-&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Findiana-jones-and-the-great-circle%3Fhmb_source%3Dsearch_bar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Humble Bundle</a></span> </p><p>On November 25, <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://youtu.be/3QyAVQjLi_s&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://youtu.be/3QyAVQjLi_s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>MinnMax</em> posted a new rapid fire interview</a></span> with two of the developers on<em> Indiana Jones and the Great Circle.</em> During the interview, the devs were asked <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://youtu.be/3QyAVQjLi_s?t=520&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://youtu.be/3QyAVQjLi_s?t=520" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">how long <em>The Great Circle </em>is</a></span> and while they didn’t give a specific hour count, they did provide some context that lets us come up with a rough estimation. </p><h2 id="h98209"><a id=""></a>How long is Indiana Jones and the Great Circle? </h2><p>“By far this is the biggest and longest game that MachineGames have ever done,” said<em> Great Circle</em>’s creative director Axel Torvenius. </p><p><span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MachineGames#Games_developed&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MachineGames#Games_developed" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MachineGames’ previous “biggest” titles</a></span> include the very good <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/wolfenstein-the-new-order-the-kotaku-review-1579710698&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/wolfenstein-the-new-order-the-kotaku-review-1579710698"><em>Wolfenstein: The New Order</em></a></span> and its (also good) sequel ,<em>Wolfenstein II: The New Colossus.</em> Both were fairly large, somewhat linear shooters featuring more open-ended moments and a lot of Nazi killing. That sounds very similar to what we’re getting in <em>The Great Circle. </em><span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://howlongtobeat.com/?q=Wolfenstein&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://howlongtobeat.com/?q=Wolfenstein" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Those two games both took about 13-15 hours</a></span> to complete, assuming you did some side content and didn’t just rush to the end. </p><p>It seems safe to assume that <em>Great Circle</em>, <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/indiana-jones-great-circle-bethesda-footage-1851628386?_gl=1*dtp8h8*_ga*MzQzNjkwNDM2LjE2NDY2NjQ1NzQ.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMjY0MDMwNy4zNy4xLjE3MzI2NTU2NjMuNTkuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/indiana-jones-great-circle-bethesda-footage-1851628386?_gl=1*dtp8h8*_ga*MzQzNjkwNDM2LjE2NDY2NjQ1NzQ.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMjY0MDMwNy4zNy4xLjE3MzI2NTU2NjMuNTkuMC4w">which sounds like a much bigger game with maps you can revisit to find missed secrets</a></span>, will take most players at least 16 hours or more.  Based on the fact that the game also includes nearly four hours of cutscenes, as revealed in the <em>MinnMax</em> interview, I’d say that it’s probable that <em>Great Circle</em> ends up being a 20-hour game for many people, especially if you don’t rush through levels and try to find everything secret and complete all the puzzles. </p><p>On the flip side, it would only take you about <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.merchoid.com/blog/post/how-long-would-it-take-to-watch-every-indiana-jones-movie/#:~:text=Including%20The%20Dial,and%202%20minutes.&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.merchoid.com/blog/post/how-long-would-it-take-to-watch-every-indiana-jones-movie/#:~:text=Including%20The%20Dial,and%202%20minutes." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1o hours to watch all five <em>Indiana Jones</em> movies</a></span>. Will this new game feel like five <em>Indiana Jones</em> movies smooshed together? We’ll find out soon enough. </p><p><em>Indiana Jones and the Great Circle </em>launches on Xbox, Game Pass, and PC on December 9. If you pre-order the fancy expensive version, you get to play it three days early. <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/indiana-jones-great-circle-game-pass-ps5-exclusive-1851626140&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/indiana-jones-great-circle-game-pass-ps5-exclusive-1851626140">The game will also arrive on PlayStation 5 next year</a></span>. </p><p><strong>Pre-order <em>Indiana Jones and the Great Circle: </em></strong><span><a data-ga="[]" href="https://www.amazon.com/Indiana-Jones-Great-Circle-Xbox-X/dp/B0DDRCNCHC/ref=sr_1_1?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://kotaku.com/how-long-is-indiana-jones-great-circle-xbox-game-pass-1851708781&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim" data-vtas-click="self:InlineUrl:inline-url-postbody" data-amazonasin="B0DDRCNCHC" data-amazontag="kinjakotakulink-20">Amazon</a></span> | <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://howl.link/o5gjvwl4kpjle&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://howl.link/o5gjvwl4kpjle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Best Buy</a></span> | <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://humblebundleinc.sjv.io/c/379647/2059850/25796?subId1=KT-&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Findiana-jones-and-the-great-circle%3Fhmb_source%3Dsearch_bar&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://humblebundleinc.sjv.io/c/379647/2059850/25796?subId1=KT-&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Findiana-jones-and-the-great-circle%3Fhmb_source%3Dsearch_bar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Humble Bundle</a></span></p><p> .<br></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
